"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.5\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.5</span> 標題：犁、犁頭（Plow and plowshare）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אֵת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’eth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:20\">1SA 13:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:21\">1SA 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:4\">ISA 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel4:10\">JOL 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:3\">MIC 4:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： חרשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： charash（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:10\">DEU 22:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:18\">JDG 14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:12\">1SA 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:19\">1KI 19:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:14\">JOB 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:8\">JOB 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:3\">PSA 129:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:3\">PSA 129:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:4\">PRO 20:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:24\">ISA 28:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:24\">ISA 28:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:18\">JER 26:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:11\">HOS 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:13\">HOS 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:12\">AMO 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:13\">AMO 9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:12\">MIC 3:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἀροτριάω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： arotriaō（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:7\">LUK 17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:10\">1CO 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:10\">1CO 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir6:19\">SIR 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir7:12\">SIR 7:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἄροτρον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： arotron)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:62\">LUK 9:62</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir38:25\">SIR 38:25</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0319_plowing_hant.jpg\" alt=\"埃及耕犁模型\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">埃及耕犁模型 (Metropolitan Museum of Art, Public domain, MMA)</figcaption></figure>犁是一個扁平的三角形刃片（「犁頭」），由硬木或金屬製成，連接著一個把手。犁頭還有一種設計，是在木棒上面包著一個圓柱形的帶尖金屬套筒。把手上面繫著繩子或木棒，然後與軛連在一起，由一隻或多隻牲畜牽拉。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>犁用來破開土壤，為播種或種植幼苗做準備。撒好種子後，有時會再次翻耕土壤來蓋住種子，以免被鳥吃掉或被太陽曬死。犁頭的尖端會在地上破開一道淺溝。犁並不翻起土壤，只是破開土地表層，深度很少超過25厘米（10英吋）。犁可以由人來拉，但更多時候是用牛或驢，人走在後面指揮著牲畜，同時扶住犁以掌握方向和破土深度。</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0005_plow.jpg\" alt=\"鋤犁\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">鋤犁 (© Deutsche Bibelgesellschaft, Stuttgart by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>有學者提出，<em>’eth</em> 是一種在真正耕犁之前劃開土壤的銳利農具。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在世界大多數地區，人們至少會知道某種類型的犁。如果當地人不知道犁，翻譯者可以使用翻土所用的某種農具作為譯詞，例如「鋤頭」。但是，如果經文講的是用牲畜耕地，就不能這樣翻譯（如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:10\">DEU 22:10</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:19\">1KI 19:19</a> ）。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:4\">ISA 2:4</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel4:10\">JOL 4:10</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:3\">MIC 4:3</a> 中，<em>’eth</em> 強調的是犁頭和刀在外形上很相似。如果目標語言文化不知道犁，翻譯者在這些經文中可以用其他農具來替代，不過這種農具應該可以很合理地用劍、大砍刀或彎刀改鑄而成。</p>\n<p>希伯來文動詞<em>charash</em> 在幾處經文中是比喻用法。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:18\">JER 26:18</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:12\">MIC 3:12</a> ，這個詞說的是耶路撒冷被完全毀滅；在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:8\">JOB 4:8</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:13\">HOS 10:13</a> ，這個詞的意思是行惡將帶來惡果。關於耕犁在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:3\">PSA 129:3</a> 中的比喻用法，參《〈詩篇〉手冊》（<em>A Handbook on Psalms</em> ）第1080頁。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
